38 /**
39  * @brief Seeds the pseudo-random number generator used by rand()
40  */
41 
42 void setUp(void)
43 {
44  uint64_t seed;
45  static int n;
46 
47 #if HAS_TIME_H
48  seed = (uint64_t)(time(NULL) ^ getpid() ^ (intptr_t)&setUp);
49 #else
50  seed = 1;
51 #endif
52 
53  if (!n) {
54  n = 1;
55  cmp_rand_seed(seed);
56  printf("seed: %"PRIu64"\n", seed);
57  }
58 }

61 /**
62  * @test cmp_cfg_icu_create

64 
65 void test_cmp_cfg_icu_create(void)
66 {
67  struct cmp_cfg cfg;
68  enum cmp_data_type data_type;
69  enum cmp_mode cmp_mode;
70  uint32_t model_value, lossy_par;
71  const enum cmp_data_type biggest_data_type = DATA_TYPE_F_CAM_BACKGROUND;
72 
73  /* wrong data type tests */
74  data_type = DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN; /* not valid data type */
75  cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_RAW;
76  model_value = 0;
77  lossy_par = CMP_LOSSLESS;
78  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
79  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
80  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
81 
82  data_type = biggest_data_type + 1; /* not valid data type */
83  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
84  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
85  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
86 
87  data_type = biggest_data_type;
88  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
89  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(biggest_data_type, cfg.data_type);
90  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_RAW, cfg.cmp_mode);
91  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.model_value);
92  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.round);
93  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
94  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
95 
96  /* this should work */
97  data_type = DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE;
98  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
99  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, cfg.data_type);
100  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_RAW, cfg.cmp_mode);
101  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.model_value);
102  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.round);
103  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
104  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
105 
106  /* wrong compression mode tests */
107  cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_STUFF + 1;
108  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
109  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
110  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
111 
112  cmp_mode = (enum cmp_mode)-1;
113  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
114  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
115  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
116 
117  /* this should work */
118  cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_STUFF;
119  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
120  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, cfg.data_type);
121  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_STUFF, cfg.cmp_mode);
122  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.model_value);
123  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.round);
124  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
125  memset(&cfg, 0, sizeof(cfg));
126 
127  /* wrong model_value tests */
128  cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_MODEL_MULTI; /* model value checks only active on model mode */
129  model_value = MAX_MODEL_VALUE + 1;
130  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
131  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
132 
133  model_value = -1U;
134  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
135  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
136 
137  /* this should work */
138  model_value = MAX_MODEL_VALUE;
139  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
140  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, cfg.data_type);
141  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_MODEL_MULTI, cfg.cmp_mode);
142  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(16, cfg.model_value);
143  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.round);
144  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
145 
146  /* no checks for model mode -> no model cmp_mode */
147  cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_STUFF;
148  model_value = MAX_MODEL_VALUE + 1;
149  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
150  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, cfg.data_type);
151  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_STUFF, cfg.cmp_mode);
152  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(MAX_MODEL_VALUE + 1, cfg.model_value);
153  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(0, cfg.round);
154  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
155  model_value = MAX_MODEL_VALUE;
156 
157  /* wrong lossy_par tests */
158  lossy_par = MAX_ICU_ROUND + 1;
159  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
160  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
161 
162  lossy_par = -1U;
163  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
164  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN, cfg.data_type);
165 
166  /* this should work */
167  lossy_par = MAX_ICU_ROUND;
168  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
169  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, cfg.data_type);
170  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(CMP_MODE_STUFF, cfg.cmp_mode);
171  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(16, cfg.model_value);
172  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(3, cfg.round);
173  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
174 
175  /* random test */
176  data_type = cmp_rand_between(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, biggest_data_type);
177  cmp_mode = cmp_rand_between(CMP_MODE_RAW, CMP_MODE_STUFF);
178  model_value = cmp_rand_between(0, MAX_MODEL_VALUE);
179  lossy_par = cmp_rand_between(CMP_LOSSLESS, MAX_ICU_ROUND);
180  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(data_type, cmp_mode, model_value, lossy_par);
181  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(data_type, cfg.data_type);
182  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_mode, cfg.cmp_mode);
183  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(model_value, cfg.model_value);
184  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(lossy_par, cfg.round);
185  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE, cfg.max_used_bits);
186 }

218  compressed_data_len_samples);
219  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_size_t(0, s);
220 
221  /* error case: no data test */

223  data_to_compress = NULL; /* no data set */
224  data_samples = 4;
225  model_of_data = NULL;
226  updated_model = NULL;
227  compressed_data = cmp_data;

229  s = cmp_cfg_icu_buffers(&cfg, data_to_compress, data_samples,
230  model_of_data, updated_model, compressed_data,
231  compressed_data_len_samples);
232  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_size_t(0, s);
233 
234  /* now its should work */
235  cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, CMP_MODE_DIFF_ZERO, 16, CMP_LOSSLESS);
236  data_to_compress = ima_data;
237  s = cmp_cfg_icu_buffers(&cfg, data_to_compress, data_samples,
238  model_of_data, updated_model, compressed_data,
239  compressed_data_len_samples);
240  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_size_t(8, s);

242  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(NULL, cfg.model_buf);
243  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(4, cfg.samples);
244  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(NULL, cfg.icu_new_model_buf);
245  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(cmp_data, cfg.icu_output_buf);
246  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(4, cfg.buffer_length);
247 
248  /* error case: model mode and no model */

250  model_of_data = NULL;
251  s = cmp_cfg_icu_buffers(&cfg, data_to_compress, data_samples,
252  model_of_data, updated_model, compressed_data,
253  compressed_data_len_samples);
254  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_size_t(0, s);
255 
256  /* now its should work */

258  model_of_data = ima_model;

269  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(4, cfg.buffer_length);

271  /* error case: data == model */

273  data_to_compress = ima_data;

451 /**
452  * @test cmp_cfg_icu_max_used_bits
453  */
454 
455 void test_cmp_cfg_icu_max_used_bits(void)
456 {
457  int error;
458  struct cmp_cfg cfg = cmp_cfg_icu_create(DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE, CMP_MODE_MODEL_ZERO, 0, CMP_LOSSLESS);
459  struct cmp_max_used_bits max_used_bits = MAX_USED_BITS_SAFE;
460 
461  error = cmp_cfg_icu_max_used_bits(&cfg, &max_used_bits);
462  TEST_ASSERT_FALSE(error);
463  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(&max_used_bits, cfg.max_used_bits);
464 
465  /* error cases */
466  max_used_bits.s_fx = 33; /* this value is to big */
467  error = cmp_cfg_icu_max_used_bits(&cfg, &max_used_bits);
468  TEST_ASSERT_TRUE(error);
469  max_used_bits.s_fx = 1;
470 
471  error = cmp_cfg_icu_max_used_bits(NULL, &max_used_bits);

4249 
4250 void test_pad_bitstream(void)
4251 {
4252  struct cmp_cfg cfg = {0};
4253  int cmp_size;
4254  int cmp_size_return;
4255  uint32_t cmp_data[3];
4256  const int MAX_BIT_LEN = 96;
4257 
4258  memset(cmp_data, 0xFF, sizeof(cmp_data));
4259  cfg.icu_output_buf = cmp_data;
4260  cfg.data_type = DATA_TYPE_IMAGETTE; /* 16 bit samples */
4261  cfg.buffer_length = 6; /* 6 * 16 bit samples -> 3 * 32 bit */
4262 
4263  /* test negative cmp_size */
4264  cmp_size = -1;
4265  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
4266  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(-1, cmp_size_return);
4267  cmp_size = -3;
4268  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
4269  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(-3, cmp_size_return);
4270 
4271  /* test RAW_MODE */
4272  cfg.cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_RAW;
4273  cmp_size = MAX_BIT_LEN;
4274  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
4275  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(MAX_BIT_LEN, cmp_size_return);
4276  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[0], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4277  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[1], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4278  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[2], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4279 
4280  /* test Normal operation */
4281  cfg.cmp_mode = CMP_MODE_MODEL_MULTI;
4282  cmp_size = 0;
4283  /* set the first 32 bits zero no change should occur */
4284  cmp_size = put_n_bits32(0, 32, cmp_size, cfg.icu_output_buf, MAX_BIT_LEN);
4285  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
4286  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_size, cmp_size_return);
4287  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[0], 0);
4288  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[1], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4289  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[2], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4290 
4291  /* set the first 33 bits zero; and checks the padding */
4292  cmp_size = put_n_bits32(0, 1, cmp_size, cfg.icu_output_buf, MAX_BIT_LEN);
4293  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
4294  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_size, cmp_size_return);
4295  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[0], 0);
4296  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[1], 0);
4297  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_INT(cmp_data[2], 0xFFFFFFFF);
4298 
4299  /* set the first 63 bits zero; and checks the padding */
4300  cmp_data[1] = 0xFFFFFFFF;
4301  cmp_size = 32;
4302  cmp_size = put_n_bits32(0, 31, cmp_size, cfg.icu_output_buf, MAX_BIT_LEN);
4303  cmp_size_return = pad_bitstream(&cfg, cmp_size);
